Uses of ServiceResources in org.greatage.ioc
 

Classes in org.greatage.ioc that implement ServiceResources
 class ServiceAdditionalResources<T>
          This class represents ServiceResources proxy implementation that is used for extending its default functionality by adding additional resources.
 class ServiceBuildResources<T>
          This class represents service resources proxy that is used during service build phase and adds resulting service configuration as additional resource.
 class ServiceConfigureResources<T>
          This class represents service resources proxy that is used during service configure phase and adds service configuration as additional resource.
 class ServiceDecorateResources<T>
          This class represents service resources proxy that is used during service decorate phase and adds service instance as additional resource.
 class ServiceInitialResources<T>
          This class represents default ServiceResources implementation that is used for retrieving default service resources such as other services, symbols or specific service logger instance.
